&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Launchpad Technologies Inc. &lt;/strong&gt;is a global technology partner connecting top talent with high-impact projects across North America and beyond. We specialize in Staff Augmentation and product development, helping companies scale with agility while empowering professionals to grow in meaningful, remote-first environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have you started your career in Finance, Accounting, Accounts Payable, Procurement, or Business Administration and later discovered that you enjoyed implementing financial systems more than running the processes themselves? Maybe you began as an Accountant, AP Analyst, Financial Analyst, Procurement Specialist, or Business Consultant before transitioning into ERP or SaaS implementations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you understand financial operations because you&#39;ve actually worked in them, and now enjoy helping customers transform those processes through technology, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are partnering with a global leader in cloud-based Spend Management and Accounts Payable Automation solutions trusted by thousands of organizations worldwide. As part of this strategic partnership, we&#39;re building a specialized Professional Services team that will guide international customers through the successful implementation of the AP Automation platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a customer-facing consulting role where you&#39;ll combine your finance knowledge, analytical thinking, and implementation experience to help organizations modernize the way they purchase, approve invoices, manage suppliers, and automate financial operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote data-start=&quot;793&quot; data-end=&quot;1002&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;795&quot; data-end=&quot;1002&quot;&gt;🗓&amp;nbsp; &lt;strong data-start=&quot;798&quot; data-end=&quot;812&quot;&gt;Start date&lt;/strong&gt;: Not defined - &lt;em&gt;We are continuously adding new members to this growing team&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;836&quot; data-end=&quot;839&quot;&gt;📆 &lt;strong data-start=&quot;844&quot; data-end=&quot;861&quot;&gt;Contract type&lt;/strong&gt;: Contractor, Full-Time, 100% Remote&lt;br data-start=&quot;906&quot; data-end=&quot;909&quot;&gt;🌐 &lt;strong data-start=&quot;914&quot; data-end=&quot;928&quot;&gt;Work hours&lt;/strong&gt;: Monday to Friday, 7.30 am to 4.30 pm PST&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1004&quot; data-end=&quot;1007&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1009&quot; data-end=&quot;1036&quot;&gt;What You’ll Be Doing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Functional Consultant, you&#39;ll become a trusted advisor for customers.&amp;nbsp;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding customers&#39; finance and procurement processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading discovery sessions to identify business requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translating business needs into system configuration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configuring the platform following implementation best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advising customers on process improvements and automation opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting User Acceptance Testing (UAT), training sessions, and Go-Live activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Helping customers successfully adopt the platform and maximize business value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explaining new product features and their impact on business processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with Project Managers, Technical Consultants, Product Specialists, and Customer Success teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing multiple implementation projects simultaneously while maintaining excellent customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
