&lt;h3&gt;About the Role - Lead Platform Engineer (Azure)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Build the platform behind one of the world&#39;s most iconic travel experiences. &lt;/em&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Lead Platform Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; who enjoys building cloud platforms the right way, not just keeping them running.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll lead the evolution of our client&#39;s &lt;strong&gt;Azure&lt;/strong&gt; platform, helping modernize cloud infrastructure, define engineering standards, and guide the migration of production workloads into a scalable, secure, and well-governed architecture. This is a highly technical leadership role where you&#39;ll influence architecture decisions from day one, mentor engineers, and establish the platform foundations that future products will rely on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy solving complex cloud challenges, designing resilient systems, and driving engineering excellence, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📅Start date: ASAP&lt;br&gt;🖋️Contract type: Full-time / Contractor&lt;br&gt;🕘Work hours: Monday to Friday, 8 AM to 5 PM PST&lt;br&gt;💻Work mode: 100% remote&lt;/p&gt;
